Class AutoscopeDriverFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • autoscope.driver.AutoscopeDriverFactory

  • public class AutoscopeDriverFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Determines which Autoscope driver to use, sets capabilities, virtual devices, simulators, and starts the Appium server.
